#: ../../../prop_sf/COMPILE_DEFINITIONS_CONFIG.rst:2
msgid "COMPILE_DEFINITIONS_<CONFIG>"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_sf/COMPILE_DEFINITIONS_CONFIG.rst:6
msgid ""
"Prefer the :prop_sf:`COMPILE_DEFINITIONS` source-file property with :manual:"
"`generator expressions <cmake-generator-expressions(7)>`."
msgstr ""
"建議使用搭配 :manual:`生成器表達式 <cmake-generator-expressions(7)>` 的 :"
"prop_sf:`COMPILE_DEFINITIONS` 來源檔案屬性。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/COMPILE_DEFINITIONS_CONFIG.rst:9
msgid "Per-configuration preprocessor definitions on a source file."
msgstr "來源檔案上各組態的預處理器定義。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/COMPILE_DEFINITIONS_CONFIG.rst:11
msgid ""
"This is the configuration-specific version of :prop_sf:`COMPILE_DEFINITIONS`."
msgstr "這是 :prop_sf:`COMPILE_DEFINITIONS` 的特定組態版本。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/COMPILE_DEFINITIONS_CONFIG.rst:13
msgid ""
"Note that :generator:`Xcode` does not support per-configuration source file "
"flags so this property will be ignored by the :generator:`Xcode` generator."
msgstr ""
"請注意，:generator:`Xcode` 不支援依組態的來源檔案旗標，因此 :generator:"
"`Xcode` 生成器將忽略此屬性。"
